#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php
msgid "Step 1: Create BunnyCDN Account"
msgstr "步驟 1：建立 BunnyCDN 帳號"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php
msgid ""
"If you don't have a BunnyCDN account yet, visit the BunnyCDN website and "
"create a new account."
msgstr "若您尚無 BunnyCDN 帳號，請前往 BunnyCDN 網站建立新帳號。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php
msgid "Visit BunnyCDN"
msgstr "前往 BunnyCDN"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Step 2: Access Account Settings"
msgstr "步驟 2：進入帳號設定"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"Once logged in, navigate to your account settings to find the API section."
msgstr "登入後，前往帳號設定以找到 API 區段。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"Click on profile icon of the top left and select Account Settings then API "
"Key from the menu in your BunnyCDN dashboard."
msgstr ""
"點擊左上角的個人資料圖示，在 BunnyCDN 儀表板選單中選擇「帳號設定」，再選"
"「API Key」。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Get API Key"
msgstr "取得 API Key"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Step 3: Copy API Key"
msgstr "步驟 3：複製 API Key"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"In the API section, generate a new API key or copy your existing one. This "
"key will be used to authenticate API requests."
msgstr ""
"在 API 區段中，產生新的 API Key 或複製現有金鑰。此金鑰將用於驗證 API 請求。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Keep this API key secure and never share it publicly."
msgstr "請妥善保管此 API Key，切勿公開分享。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Step 4: Create Stream Library"
msgstr "步驟 4：建立 Stream 媒體庫"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"Create a new Stream library in your BunnyCDN dashboard if you haven't "
"already. This is where your videos will be stored."
msgstr ""
"若尚未建立，請在 BunnyCDN 儀表板建立新的 Stream 媒體庫，影片將儲存於此。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "You can create multiple libraries for different projects or purposes."
msgstr "您可以針對不同專案或用途建立多個媒體庫。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php
msgid "Step 5: Configure Integration"
msgstr "步驟 5：設定整合"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"Enter your API key in the field below and enable the integration. The system "
"will automatically test the connection."
msgstr "在以下欄位輸入您的 API Key 並啟用整合，系統將自動測試連線。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php
msgid "Step 6: Secure Your Videos (Optional)"
msgstr ""

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"To protect your videos with signed URLs, enable Token Authentication on your "
"Stream library in the BunnyCDN dashboard. FluentPlayer will automatically "
"sign all video requests."
msgstr ""

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"Go to Stream → Your Library → Security → Enable \"Token Authentication\"."
msgstr ""

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Step 7: Configure Allowed Referrers"
msgstr ""

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"If you enable \"Block None Referrer\" on your Stream library, you must add "
"your website domain to the Allowed Referrers list, otherwise all video "
"requests will be blocked."
msgstr ""

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid ""
"Go to Stream → Your Library → Security → Allowed Referrers → Add your domain "
"(e.g., yourdomain.com)."
msgstr ""

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Step 8: Test Connection"
msgstr ""

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStorageIntegration.php
msgid ""
"After saving your settings, use the \"Test Connection\" button to verify "
"that the integration is working correctly."
msgstr "儲存設定後，使用「測試連線」按鈕驗證整合是否正常運作。"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Enable BunnyCDN Stream"
msgstr "啟用 BunnyCDN Stream"

#: app/Integrations/BunnyCDNStreamIntegration.php
msgid "Enable BunnyCDN Stream integration for video hosting"
msgstr "啟用 BunnyCDN Stream 整合以進行影片托管"

